`GL_DEPTH_COMPONENT24`, or `GL_DEPTH_COMPONENT16`, one of the combined depth-stencil formats,
`GL_DEPTH32F_STENCIL8`, or `GL_DEPTH24_STENCIL8`, or the stencil-only format,
