`GL_INT_2_10_10_10_REV`, `GL_UNSIGNED_INT_2_10_10_10_REV`, or `GL_UNSIGNED_INT_10F_11F_11F_REV`.

`GL_INVALID_ENUM` is generated if `glVertexAttribL` is used with a `type` other than
