`GL_LINE_LOOP`, `GL_LINES`, `GL_TRIANGLE_STRIP`, `GL_TRIANGLE_FAN`, or `GL_TRIANGLES`.

`GL_INVALID_VALUE` is generated if `count` or `instancecount` is negative.

